# CNPEM - Centro Nacional de Pesquisa em Energia e Materiais, Brazil
# Sirius - Research Group EMA
#
# Code project: TC_caculus
# 
# Objectif:
# Automate the use of Quantum Espresso (QE) for the calculus of critical 
# superconductivity temperature of diferent molecules and cell structures
# 
##------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#Instructions in how to use TC_calculus

#->Unpack .tar.gz
#->Open terminal in unpacked folder 
#->Open write_config.py and change variables at will
#->Remember to save the pseudo potential files you need in 'pseudo' folder and #add their names in write_config.py as previous ones

#call in terminal:

python3 program.py directory/file_name.cif

#Enjoy your TC's!!!

#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#New features:

#-> No need to run 'write.py', because it is automatically called by program.py 
#during execution
#-> Results are saved in a subdirectory named after the .cif file



